    { q: 'Can I edit my CV after publishing?', a: 'Yes. Return to the editor, change what you need and republish. Your website updates instantly.' },
    { q: 'Can I delete my CV?', a: 'Yes. Delete your GitHub repository and your CV stops being available immediately.' },
    { q: 'Can I have multiple languages?', a: 'Yes. You can create your CV in Spanish, Italian or English. Switch languages instantly.' },
    { q: 'Do I need to install anything?', a: 'No. It works directly in the browser. You don\'t need to download or install any software.' },
    { q: 'What happens if GitHub changes?', a: 'You always have a copy of your data in standard format. You can migrate to any JSON Resume-compatible service.' },
    { q: 'Why is it better than a traditional editor?', a: 'Because it separates data from design. In Word or Canva, every change can break the format. Here, you change what you want and the design always stays intact.' }
